&lt;/ul&gt; 
&lt;p&gt;Everything here is structured around a single goal: giving marketing teams a repeatable, data-driven framework that ties AI search visibility directly to pipeline and revenue impact — anchored by HubSpot AEO. Let’s get started.&lt;/p&gt; 
